casebody.data:
Friday, April 9, 1999

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

98-749. Kopich v. Kopich.

Hamilton App. No. C-970175. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
